snippet.title: Warframe | Update 12.0 Highlights
snippet.description:
Update 12.0 is almost upon us, Check out what we have in store for you!
New Warframe, New Game Modes, Expanded Tile sets, A new HUD, Mod system upgrades, and so much more.
